name: The Nursery
description:
Alice in Wonderland is a very well known story to all of us. 
Its strong characters fill our imaginary and make us travel to other universes.
This reinterpretation (with the help of AI) of the original illustrations by John Tenniel is an homage to the Wonderland of Lewis Carrol and all the wonderful things it has brought to children and adults alike. 
Enjoy Alice in AI Land Collection!
[August 2021]
